# Project Features

## 1. Responsive Design
- Fully optimized for desktop, tablet, and mobile screens.
- Uses modern CSS (Flexbox/Grid) for layout adjustments.

## 2. Clean and Modern UI
- Minimalistic design with smooth spacing and typography.
- Consistent color palette and visual hierarchy.

## 3. Structured Sections
- **Home/Hero Section:** Brief introduction and call-to-action.
- **About Me:** Personal background and goals.
- **Skills Section:** Technical and soft skills showcased visually.
- **Projects Section:** Displays completed projects with descriptions.
- **Contact Section:** Provides email/social contact options.

## 4. Fast Loading & Lightweight
- Pure HTML and CSS.
- No heavy frameworks or external dependencies.

## 5. Easy Customization
- Simple file structure for quick editing.
- Colors, fonts, images, and text can be changed easily in one place.

## 6. Semantic HTML
- Proper use of tags (`header`, `section`, `nav`, `footer`, etc.).
- Improves readability, SEO, and accessibility.

## 7. Cross-Browser Compatibility
- Works smoothly on Chrome, Edge, Firefox, and Safari.

## 8. Organized Asset Management
- Dedicated folders for images, styles, and documentation.

## 9. Clear Navigation
- Smooth scrolling through internal anchors.
- User-friendly top navigation bar.

